as a seller, i should be able to view my store

as a seller, i want to be able to see my store reviews

as a seller, i want to be able to see the orders i got

as a seller, i want to be able to see my store analytics

as a seller, i want to be able to deregister as a seller 

as a seller, i want to be able to see my top selling product

as a buyer, i want to be able to click checkout button to pay for my cart

as a buyer, i want to be able to review a product i bought

as a buyer, i want to be able to delete my account

